CustomerController -[hidden]down- POSController
POSController -[hidden]down- SelfCheckoutController
SelfCheckoutController -[hidden]down- PromotionController
PromotionController -[hidden]down- StatsController

note right of BaseEntity
DELETE logique:
les donnees restent en base texte,
on passe seulement active=false.
end note

note right of SearchNormalizer
Recherche partielle:
- ignore accents
- ignore maj/min
- "em" => Emilie, Emma, Emmanuelle
end note

note right of SeedDataService
Charge au demarrage un jeu de donnees
minimum de 10 enregistrements
par module principal.
end note

@enduml
